task.summary: Adding implementation of Singly Linked List
Added Polynomial application of Singly Linked List along with its test cases
Removed binary class files and added comments
Added the code for finding the middle element in a linked list and its test cases
Added the code for finding the loop, finding the length of the loop if exists and removing the loop in the linked list. Test cases for the same are also added
Added the code for Nth node from the start and from the end in the linked list. Test cases for the same are also added
Added the code for checking if the singly linked list is palindrome or not. Test cases for the same are also added.
Added the code for removing duplicates from the sorted and unsorted linked list. Test cases for the same are also added.
Added the code for swapping nodes in the linked list. Test cases for the same are also added.
Added the code for creating union and intersection of two lists. Test cases for the same are also added.
Added the code for finding the intersection point of two lists. Test cases for the same are also added.
